This procedure describes how to configure Edge System components using command prompt.

1. 	
Open a command prompt.
2. 	
Navigate to the Edge System installation directory: %Program Files%/OSIsoft/EdgeSystem.
3. 	
To configure a component, run this command:

.\OSIsoft.Data.System.Host.exe configuration system components componentId=componentId componentType=componentType

4. 	
To view configured components, run this command:

.\OSIsoft.Data.System.Host.exe configuration system components
